        <h2 class="h2">Why a Charter?</h2>
        <p>There are lots of dedicated people across Manchester who are working hard to support people who are homeless, and many more who would like to do something to help. The Charter is a way to bring us all together with a shared vision, so that we can focus our efforts effectively to tackle key challenges, and ultimately to end homelessness.</p>
