        <h2 class="h2 superhero__header block--priority">When is the launch?</h2>
        <p>The Charter will launch on 9th May at Friend’s Meeting House.</p>
        <p>Presented by the Bishop of Manchester and attended by Richard Leese, leader of Manchester City Council, this will be a historic event which celebrates the commitment of our city’s people, organisations and businesses to tackling homelessness. There will be a symbolic handing over from the Manchester Homelessness Partnership to the city, and opportunities to pledge your support and join an action group too.</p>
